hopobject.body: We'll need to take up references buy valtrex in uk Director James Cameron (Titanic) is the master of overblown, epic entertainment, and this is one of his most ludicrously audacious efforts: one city–centre chase sequence concludes with Arnold Schwarzenegger in a hotel lift – on horseback. Arnie plays a secret agent who is kidnapped by nuclear terrorists along with his wife (Jamie Lee Curtis). Armageddon comes to Florida, and the mayhem is magnificent.
